{{Politics of Sudan}} The '''Vice President of Sudan''' is the second highest [[political]] position obtainable in [[Sudan]]. Currently there is a provision for two Vice Presidents, who are appointed by the [[List of heads of state of Sudan|President of Sudan]]. Historically either the First or the Second Vice President was from [[Southern Sudan Autonomous Region (1972–83)|Southern Sudan]].
